social_posts.post_text:
Mahalo 🌺🌴

A truly magical way to end 2022 with great friends and the nature Maui has to offer.

24 EMOM 
1. 10 Power Snatches 75#
2. 15 Burpees
3. 14 Cal row

Min 24-30
1 RM Snatch 

Brutal workout today @westlaathletics , but I’m committed to being fit AF for this years CrossFit Open. Now, I am no fan of “new year, new me” more so having a goal to work towards at any point during the year. But who can resist a New Year Resolution?!

What’s your fitness goal?! LETS GO!

#Upfor2023 #ascentpartner @ascent_protein

More reps! 14.4 —> 23.1
Back in 2014 I preformed my first ring muscle ups during this Open workout. Upon @crossfitgames bringing it back this year, I’m happy to report I’ve improved since the previous attempt! Still caused the same agony 🤦🏼‍♀️ but at least I still had my same coach/judge @jessicasuver 🫶🏼 keeping my head screwed on.

Rain dance.
Thank you Mother Nature for giving California luscious atmospheric rivers. Your generosity hasn’t been unnoticed or gone to waste!

Quarter Finals

At the beginning of this year I decided against reaching for a Games spot. The extra effort and time spent grinding and training weakness wasn’t appealing. And yet, 3, 2, 1, GO never fails to spark the most fierce competitor in me. I’m incredibly stoked to have ranked as high as I did, given my heart wasn’t fully in it. 
*Bittersweet feelings* 
Next up, I’ll maintain my fitness as I travel, say yes to everything and spend my summer in a bikini 🙋🏼‍♀️👙🌞

Thank you @jessicasuver the greatest coach of all time. @man_unbound for the assist. @westlaathletics for being the training ground for a stellar group of competitors. ⚡️⚡️⚡️ @ascent_protein #athleteforlife
Friday happy hour clean and jerks.

This is us.

Imperfect, rowdy, competitive, devoted and full of love for each other. We may all be on different life paths but we choose to come together to celebrate our blood line. DANG family rules! #DANGgang

Sayulita x Birthdarette 
Proper celebration it was!
Humming to the neon of the universal sound.

Coach, lover, Betty. Dodgers 💙
